    "notes": "## Experimental Build v1.15.0-hermes1\n\n**\u26a0\ufe0f Unofficial experimental build \u2014 use at your own risk.**\n\n### What's Changed\n- **ESP32 Blob Storage Optimization**: Replaced per-key files in /bl/&lt;hex&gt; with single /adv_blobs file (BlobRec records). Saves ~30 KB Flash on devices with 160 contacts. One-time migration on first boot.\n- T-Beam SX1262/SX1276 added to CI build matrix.\n- CI build check passing for all major platforms (ESP32, NRF52, RP2040).\n\n### Supported Platforms\n- ESP32 (T-Beam SX1262/SX1276, Heltec v3, etc.)\n- ESP32-C6 (T-Lora C6)\n- RP2040 (PicoW)\n- Limited NRF52/RP2040 STM32 (binaries only \u2014 UF2 conversion issue, fix pending)\n\n### Known Issues\n- NRF52/RP2040/STM32: UF2 files not generated (toolchain compatibility issue with local PlatformIO)\n- wio-e5-mini: SubGhz.h missing (upstream STM32WL issue)",
